Hierro lived in his home,
admiring his gems and precious stones...

Until one day, something caused a stir.
Intruders were coming to take his treasure...

Defend his dwelling, defend it fast.
Removing the torches, from their path...

Darkness his friend, filled his house.
He could see the heat that they gave out...

Picking them off, one by one.
Like a thief, it had to be done...

He drove them off, from his house.
But they would come back, for another bout...

They brought a wizard, who set a trap.
To teleport Hierro all the way back...

All the way back, to the bottom of the cave,
He would have to find his way...

To the exit, not easy to find.
Hierro searched for a very long time...

He sees the exit, it is so near.
But it is just as he feared...

He could not leave, because of the spell.
It trapped him there, his home now his hell...

Gone from his home, his gems and stones.
Whatever happened to Hierro, no one knows.
endmsg
